<bibRefCitation author="HENDRIXSON" box="[1256,1437,1434,1455]" pageId="39" pageNumber="38" pagination="33 - 120" refId="ref33409" refString="HENDRIXSON, B. E. 2006. Buthid scorpions of Saudi Arabia, with notes on other families (Scorpiones: Buthidae, Liochelidae, Scorpionidae). Fauna of Arabia, 21: 33 - 120." type="journal article" year="2006">Hendrixson, 2006</bibRefCitation>
